.TH LOA-PROGRESS 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
progress \- Set current page progress
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> progress
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for a book reference (ID, ISBN, title, or author) and current page.
.TP
Progress cannot be negative or exceed total pages when pages are known.
.TP
Reaching full pages marks the book as read automatically.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> progress
